snippet.title: Legend of Zelda: Super Replay - Episode 1
snippet.description:
Jeff Cork, Bryan Vore, and Dan Ryckert sit down in an ongoing series of videos in an attempt to conquer the first Zelda.

Watch the full series here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL3F93A32C201A87C9
